{
  "stem": "1603.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at this time when the revolution was over in '56.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I said, OK, you are afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this Free Europe radio, I'm going to give the signal if they killed me or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if they didn't kill me, I hope you are coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So with my truck and these 32 people, we made it to the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got arrested the first attempt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walked 15 miles, and we got arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we spent one night in jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But so many thousands of people were-- were trying to escape and so many were arrested, there was no room in the jails.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if they-- they interrogated each of us, and they questioned us who we are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if they didn't think that we are the people who are going to go out and shoot them and get-- then they let us go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they put us-- our name on a list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, Peter Fischl, you can go home to Budapest, but if we-- if we catch you one more time, you are on this list, you're going to Siberia, which is a cold place in Russia, and you're going to spend the rest of your life there.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went out to the train station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is again something interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because there was about, I don't know, 5,000 people, dirty, unshaven, you know, looked like all homeless-- we would be homeless people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Except there was one couple who looked like they just stepped out from Fifth Avenue store, beautifully dressed, combed, hat and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I-- my mind told me, these people, this is the first time they want to escape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "These people are out of their mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
